{"ayat_mp3":"https://everyayah.com/data/Alafasy_128kbps/002221.mp3","arabic":"وَلَا تَنكِحُواْ ٱلۡمُشۡرِكَٰتِ حَتَّىٰ يُؤۡمِنَّۚ وَلَأَمَةٞ مُّؤۡمِنَةٌ خَيۡرٞ مِّن مُّشۡرِكَةٖ وَلَوۡ أَعۡجَبَتۡكُمۡۗ وَلَا تُنكِحُواْ ٱلۡمُشۡرِكِينَ حَتَّىٰ يُؤۡمِنُواْۚ وَلَعَبۡدٞ مُّؤۡمِنٌ خَيۡرٞ مِّن مُّشۡرِكٖ وَلَوۡ أَعۡجَبَكُمۡۗ أُوْلَٰٓئِكَ يَدۡعُونَ إِلَى ٱلنَّارِۖ وَٱللَّهُ يَدۡعُوٓاْ إِلَى ٱلۡجَنَّةِ وَٱلۡمَغۡفِرَةِ بِإِذۡنِهِۦۖ وَيُبَيِّنُ ءَايَٰتِهِۦ لِلنَّاسِ لَعَلَّهُمۡ يَتَذَكَّرُونَ","bengali":"আর তোমরা মুশরেক নারীদেরকে বিয়ে করোনা, যতক্ষণ না তারা ঈমান গ্রহণ করে। অবশ্য মুসলমান ক্রীতদাসী মুশরেক নারী অপেক্ষা উত্তম, যদিও তাদেরকে তোমাদের কাছে ভালো লাগে। এবং তোমরা (নারীরা) কোন মুশরেকের সঙ্গে বিবাহ বন্ধনে আবদ্ধ হয়ো না, যে পর্যন্ত সে ঈমান না আনে। একজন মুসলমান ক্রীতদাসও একজন মুশরেকের তুলনায় অনেক ভাল, যদিও তোমরা তাদের দেখে মোহিত হও। তারা দোযখের দিকে আহ্বান করে, আর আল্লাহ নিজের হুকুমের মাধ্যমে আহ্বান করেন জান্নাত ও ক্ষমার দিকে। আর তিনি মানুষকে নিজের নির্দেশ বাতলে দেন যাতে তারা উপদেশ গ্রহণ করে।","english":"And do not marry Al-Mushrikat (idolatresses, etc.) till they believe (worship Allah Alone). And indeed a slave woman who believes is better than a (free) Mushrikah (idolatress, etc.), even though she pleases you. And give not (your daughters) in marriage to Al-Mushrikun till they believe (in Allah Alone) and verily, a believing slave is better than a (free) Mushrik (idolater, etc.), even though he pleases you. Those (Al-Mushrikun) invite you to the Fire, but Allah invites (you) to Paradise and Forgiveness by His Leave, and makes His Ayat (proofs, evidences, verses, lessons, signs, revelations, etc.) clear to mankind that they may remember","wbw":[{"bengali":"এবং না","english":"And (do) not","en_t":"wala","arabic":"وَلَا","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_221_001.mp3"},{"bengali":"তোমরা বিয়ে করো","english":"[you] marry","en_t":"tankihu","arabic":"تَنكِحُواْ","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_221_002.mp3"},{"bengali":"মুশরিক নারীদেরকে","english":"[the] polytheistic women","en_t":"al-mush'rikati","arabic":"ٱلۡمُشۡرِكَٰتِ","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_221_003.mp3"},{"bengali":"যতক্ষণ না","english":"until","en_t":"hatta","arabic":"حَتَّىٰ","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_221_004.mp3"},{"bengali":"ঈমান আনে","english":"they believe","en_t":"yu'minna","arabic":"يُؤۡمِنَّۚ","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_221_005.mp3"},{"bengali":"এবং অবশ্যই ক্রীতদাসী","english":"And a bondwoman","en_t":"wala-amatun","arabic":"وَلَأَمَةٞ","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_221_006.mp3"},{"bengali":"মুমিন নারী","english":"(who is) believing","en_t":"mu'minatun","arabic":"مُّؤۡمِنَةٌ","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_221_007.mp3"},{"bengali":"উত্তম","english":"(is) better","en_t":"khayrun","arabic":"خَيۡرٞ","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_221_008.mp3"},{"bengali":"থেকে","english":"than","en_t":"min","arabic":"مِّن","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_221_009.mp3"},{"bengali":"মুশরিক নারী","english":"a polytheistic woman","en_t":"mush'rikatin","arabic":"مُّشۡرِكَةٖ","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_221_010.mp3"},{"bengali":"এবং যদিও","english":"[and] even if","en_t":"walaw","arabic":"وَلَوۡ","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_221_011.mp3"},{"bengali":"তোমাদের মুগ্ধ করে সে","english":"she pleases you","en_t":"a'jabatkum","arabic":"أَعۡجَبَتۡكُمۡۗ","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_221_012.mp3"},{"bengali":"এবং না","english":"And (do) not","en_t":"wala","arabic":"وَلَا","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_221_013.mp3"},{"bengali":"তোমরা বিয়ে দিও (মুসলিম নারীকে)","english":"give in marriage (your women)","en_t":"tunkihu","arabic":"تُنكِحُواْ","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_221_014.mp3"},{"bengali":"মুশরিক পুরুষদের (সাথে)","english":"(to) [the] polytheistic men","en_t":"al-mush'rikina","arabic":"ٱلۡمُشۡرِكِينَ","ar_mp3":"https://word